rows.label: bf11640100_0010
rows.name:
Adel's star is rising.
It seems that the people love him.

rows.label: bf11640100_0022
rows.name:
...and naught but the fruit of the king's whimsy
and an obscure woman...

rows.label: bf11640100_0040
rows.name: Yet if only he were not the Driver of the Grail...

rows.label: bf11640100_0050
rows.name: ...you'd each have your just share of dignity.
